        "meta_description": "Ron Howard revealed he almost left 'Happy Days' after producers introduced an idea to change the sitcom's name to center around Henry Winkler's character Arthur 'Fonzie' Fonzarelli after he began gaining more popularity.",
        "meta_lang": "en",
